```json
{
  "application": "Slurm",
  "details": {
    "job_name": "psana_legion",
    "dependency": "singleton",
    "nodes": 33,
    "time": "03:00:00",
    "qos": "regular",
    "constraint": "knl,quad,cache",
    "core_spec": 4,
    "image": "docker:stanfordlegion/psana-mpi:latest",
    "exclusive": true,
    "mail_type": "ALL",
    "account": "m2859",
    "host_psana_dir": "$HOME/psana_legion/psana-legion",
    "host_data_dir": "$SCRATCH/noepics_c24_s1_data/reg",
    "sit_psdm_data": "$SCRATCH/noepics_c24_s1_data/reg/d/psdm",
    "eager": 1,
    "kernel_kind": "memory_bound_native",
    "rounds": [20, 40, 80, 160],
    "n": 32,
    "limit": "n * 2048",
    "c": [256, 128, 64, 32, 16],
    "nodelist": "nodelist.txt",
    "slurm_hostfile": "$PWD/nodelist.txt",
    "srun_options": "-n $(( n * c + 1 )) -N $(( n + 1 )) --cpus-per-task $(( 256 / c )) --cpu_bind threads --distribution=arbitrary --output rax_rounds\"$rounds\"_n\"$n\"_c\"$c\".log",
    "shifter_command": "$HOST_PSANA_DIR/psana_legion/scripts/psana_mpi.sh $HOST_PSANA_DIR/psana_legion/mpi_rax.py"
  }
}
```
